💬 The Messaging App Dilemma: WhatsApp vs. Telegram vs. Discord

Situation: You’re organizing a college tech fest and need to manage large groups, share files, and coordinate in real time.
Debate: Which app should be the official communication hub?

🟢 Team WhatsApp: “Ubiquity and ease of use.”

🔵 Team Telegram: “Cloud storage, channels, and large group limits.”

🟣 Team Discord: “Voice channels, bots, and organized community management.”
